724
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] I kola hitne pomoći kad su dolazile, naletli su na prometnu.

725
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo čekali, čekali, na kraju se event umjesto, ne znam, u sedam, na večer počeo u deset.

726
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, več bila predokazivanja.

727
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam imao meča, znači od 12 do 22, ono, 12 sati sam bio u dvorani i primjer sam imao meča.

728
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] Imao sam dvovo, iza polnoći, tako da.

729
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] To ubitačno, to.

730
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] Katastrofa.

731
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:32,960
[SPEAKER_01] Katastrofa.

732
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:34,960
[SPEAKER_02] Nemoš više toliko ne zagrijava tebe.

733
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ma rekao, daje samo, daje sam da se poklepam, odajem doma.

734
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:40,960
[SPEAKER_02] Sad, sad bude bilo, ono, bude sam da završim.

735
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,960
[SPEAKER_02] I onda, vajde kako sam bio, gladan sam ga nokautirao, ne znam.

736
00:35:42,960 --> 00:35:45,960
[SPEAKER_02] Žurilo ti se na večeru.

737
00:35:45,960 --> 00:35:48,960
[SPEAKER_02] Kad se glada nisi svoj.

738
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:51,960
[SPEAKER_02] Kako je bilo, ono, dževat potorak?

739
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:55,960
[SPEAKER_02] Kad je uletio, čovjek je bio na pici, znaš šta Matija?

740
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:57,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, čovjek tiše, ono, piti, ne.

741
00:35:57,960 --> 00:36:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] A nije bio gotovo, ono je radio borbu i gotovo je bilo sve.

742
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali se, ovaj, on je bio rezervna borba

743
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ovaj koji trebu ući u dalji krug, se vzlijedio i jedan i drugi.

744
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] E, ajde potorak, di je, di je, poziv za potoraka.

745
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:11,960
[SPEAKER_02] A, da, i dobro je radio, sreća se toga.

746
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] Potorak je kralj, potorak je kralj.

747
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:19,960
[SPEAKER_02] A, ajde, šta s vas...

748
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:23,960
