749
00:36:23,960 --> 00:36:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] Kako sam star jebao te?

750
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ona, zekate kuš, ne.

751
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja to ne mogu.

752
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:30,960
[SPEAKER_02] Da, na kraj bi imali, onda.

753
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:31,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ništa vidimo, sadjde.

754
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:33,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ajde bok, Igore, tamo nadesne peneš i to je to.

755
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:34,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ibaš begit ja.

756
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:35,960
