757
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Čekam da vani.

758
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:38,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ću kroz prosim.

759
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:42,960
[SPEAKER_02] Svazim sigurno formiralo ti tako i osobu i sve.

760
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,960
[SPEAKER_02] I bok si to.

761
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,960
[SPEAKER_02] Još ne, aha, koja osoba?

762
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ma je, ko osobu, puno si.

763
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:48,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pa onako.

764
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:51,960
[SPEAKER_02] Šta može recimo čovjek naučiti nakon svega toga, ono.

765
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:53,960
[SPEAKER_02] Formirate ipak to, to je poseban način života.

766
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:56,960
[SPEAKER_02] Va glej, taj spor.

767
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:59,960
