780
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:27,960
[SPEAKER_02] Zreli si, je li tako?

781
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:29,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pa, i je definitivno.

782
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:33,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, gledaj, ja bi sad povukao bi paralelu, recimo, boks kod djece.

783
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ili kickboksovom.

784
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, da, božda se zelo upotrebljava.

785
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:42,960
