791
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:05,960
[SPEAKER_02] Mada, ne, mislim, kontra je izgraditi.

792
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da se ne zelo upotrebi, jel' kaži.

793
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:11,960
[SPEAKER_02] Jer ono vam je odličan bio klip "Nasilje ostavite za ringo".

794
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,960
