807
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:35,960
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, da.

808
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:36,960
[SPEAKER_02] Čak sredi.

809
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

810
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:40,960
