00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:03,960
[SPEAKER_02] Andi, da.

826
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, je, Andi, Andi.

827
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:05,960
[SPEAKER_02] Karla Vidin, često ga.

828
00:39:05,960 --> 00:39:06,960
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

829
00:39:06,960 --> 00:39:07,960
