1205
00:56:39,960 --> 00:56:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, dobro, da lišćemo nešto.

1206
00:56:40,960 --> 00:56:42,960
[SPEAKER_02] Oba dvojce, šta bi poručili mladim borcima?

1207
00:56:42,960 --> 00:56:44,960
[SPEAKER_02] Koji sad to možda žele se okušat?

1208
00:56:44,960 --> 00:56:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] No pain, no game.

1209
00:56:46,960 --> 00:56:51,960
[SPEAKER_02] Da, ja bi ono neko, dječi, jak niste spremni na ova sva silna odricanja, nemojte ni ono, elu.

1210
00:56:51,960 --> 00:56:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mišli ti vikendu mu ne redi, cuga ovo ono i sad ću ja malo trenirati.

1211
00:56:55,960 --> 00:56:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1212
00:56:56,960 --> 00:57:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam radio prije i na pumpi, i te noćne i ono.

1213
00:57:00,960 --> 00:57:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] Noć je vrlo.

1214
00:57:01,960 --> 00:57:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] Je, gada je noć.

1215
00:57:02,960 --> 00:57:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Al ti nakon noći joj spavaš dan dva, ti si nakon dva dana ono isti kaj si bio.

1216
00:57:06,960 --> 00:57:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, kako si popiješ, pa mjesec dana treba da se vratiš u formu koja si bio, sigurno.

1217
00:57:12,960 --> 00:57:13,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

1218
00:57:13,960 --> 00:57:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] Alkogol te dehidrira i...

1219
00:57:14,960 --> 00:57:17,960
[SPEAKER_02] Naravno nema seksa, ono ništa, to mogu zaboraviti.

1220
00:57:17,960 --> 00:57:18,960
[SPEAKER_02] To mene ne interesira.

1221
00:57:18,960 --> 00:57:25,960
[SPEAKER_02] Mate, evo sad neke stvari, rečki ću 18 godina od 17. pita, Mate, ja bi se ono...

1222
00:57:25,960 --> 00:57:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] Gle, ja bi...

1223
00:57:26,960 --> 00:57:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si sad za njega već bajak užiš.

1224
00:57:28,960 --> 00:57:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ajmo reći.

1225
00:57:29,960 --> 00:57:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Osim što smo nadali, znači, konzistencija, mogla da moraš stavno trenirati, to se podrazumijeva.

1226
00:57:35,960 --> 00:57:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao bi samo od ovoga, uđi u ring i ta ćeš pravi pudu, ta ćeš upoznat svoj karakter.

1227
00:57:41,960 --> 00:57:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1228
00:57:42,960 --> 00:57:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] I nemoj se ovoga iznenaditi rezultata i istine.

1229
00:57:45,960 --> 00:57:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da jako puno ekipe žive nekakve iluzije, nikad nije to doživjelo.

1230
00:57:52,960 --> 00:57:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ti uđeš unutra, onda vidiš kad te drugi čovjek hoće ubit.

1231
00:57:55,960 --> 00:57:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] Di si, šta si.

1232
00:57:56,960 --> 00:57:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] A nećete ubit nikoga.

1233
00:57:57,960 --> 00:57:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u smislu, kao, on ćete figurativno.

1234
00:57:59,960 --> 00:58:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1235
00:58:00,960 --> 00:58:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] I stući.

1236
00:58:01,960 --> 00:58:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tu vidiš kakav si s karakterom i to je, nema ljepše stvari od tog, zato što ti znaš ko si, šta si, sad ti možeš ići prema nečem višem.

1237
00:58:08,960 --> 00:58:09,960
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

1238
00:58:09,960 --> 00:58:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je to sport, ja.

1239
00:58:10,960 --> 00:58:12,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ali najljepše što ste poslije meča opet prijatelji.

1240
00:58:12,960 --> 00:58:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] I to vidiš, meni se zna desi do ovoga, nođenko dige na spaninku, njegovu arenu dolje, on ima i nogometni teren, ima gore boksačka dvorana.

1241
00:58:22,960 --> 00:58:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sad malo za nogomet, da.

1242
00:58:24,960 --> 00:58:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kakve sve riječi ti ću još dolje na nogometu, na hakeću.

1243
00:58:28,960 --> 00:58:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je bok, to se spominje sve.

1244
00:58:30,960 --> 00:58:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se gore ubimo i kasnije grlimo.

1245
00:58:34,960 --> 00:58:39,960
[SPEAKER_02] Znački, mi imamo onu rubriku "Gost zbira temu".

1246
00:58:39,960 --> 00:58:42,960
[SPEAKER_02] To može biti poruka, to može biti nešto.

1247
00:58:42,960 --> 00:58:45,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ja joj obično ne tražim, ne želim ni znat, ako imate šta.

1248
00:58:45,960 --> 00:58:49,960
[SPEAKER_02] Možda igi kako peče kremčnite nešto na pojma ono naše.

1249
00:58:49,960 --> 00:58:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa integralne polačinke, ali sad ću mogu stati s tim.

1250
00:58:53,960 --> 00:58:55,960
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da.

1251
00:58:55,960 --> 00:58:57,960
[SPEAKER_02] Za kraj još jednom najavi događaj.

1252
00:58:57,960 --> 00:58:58,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pozovi sve.

1253
00:58:58,960 --> 00:58:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] U 6.12.

1254
00:58:59,960 --> 00:59:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] Noj gladijatora, puna dvorana, bomba, borbi.

1255
00:59:02,960 --> 00:59:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] Event će biti top.

1256
00:59:04,960 --> 00:59:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Može do sada najbolji.

1257
00:59:06,960 --> 00:59:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dobra, Igor.

1258
00:59:07,960 --> 00:59:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1259
00:59:08,960 --> 00:59:10,960
[SPEAKER_02] A ja vas pozivam da se svi preplatite na naš kanal.

1260
00:59:10,960 --> 00:59:12,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ne košta ništa.

1261
00:59:12,960 --> 00:59:14,960
[SPEAKER_02] Besplatno je i ekipa.

1262
00:59:14,960 --> 00:59:15,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ćao, dečki, vam sretno.

1263
00:59:15,960 --> 00:59:16,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pa.

1264
00:59:16,960 --> 00:59:18,960
[SPEAKER_02] Još jednom fala na pozivu, bok svima.

1265
00:59:18,960 --> 00:59:19,960
[SPEAKER_02] I drugi po.

1266
00:59:19,960 --> 00:59:20,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pa bok.

